wiki.summary: Look At Me! is the sixth single by American hip-hop recording artist XXXTENTACION. It premiered on December 31, 2015 on the SoundCloud account of Rojas, the song's co-producer, before being released for digital download on the iTunes Store as a single on January 29, 2016. It was rereleased on the Revenge mixtape on May 16, 2017, where the intro was removed. Read more on Last.fm.
